Smoke test

1. User A creates room → gets invite code


2. User B joins with code


3. Both see room in list


4. B adds item, A sees it


5. A deletes item (owner privilege) and B sees it removed



Done definition

Done = verified auth, membership permissions enforced, room sharing works, Neon data model supports real collaboration.
